      <title>9.2. ternary operator</title>
      <link>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/9.2.ternary-operator/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 09:56:46 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/9.2.ternary-operator/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; a = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; b = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;20&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; max = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (a &amp;gt; b) a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; b  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// If expression
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;println(max)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-output.txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;output.txt&#34;&gt;20
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;if가 expression 이라서, 따로 3항 연산자 없음&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html&#34;&gt;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>6.2. groupby</title>
      <link>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/6.2.groupby/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 09:56:31 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/6.2.groupby/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; numbers = listOf(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;one&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;two&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;three&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;four&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;five&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; grouped = numbers.groupBy { number &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; number[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] }  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// 첫 글자로 그룹핑
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;println(grouped)
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-output.txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;output.txt&#34;&gt;{o=[one], t=[two, three], f=[four, five]}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/collection-grouping.html&#34;&gt;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/collection-grouping.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>4.2. for-loop (with index)</title>
      <link>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/4.2.for-loop-with-index/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 09:56:12 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/4.2.for-loop-with-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; fruits = listOf(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;banana&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;mango&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; fruits.indices) {
    println(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${fruits[i]}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
}

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; ((i, fruit) &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; fruits.withIndex()) {
    println(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$fruit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
}

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;fruits.forEachIndexed { i, fruit &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    println(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$fruit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
}

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 4 (for specific range)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (i &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0.&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;) {  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// [0, 2]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;    println(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;$i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${fruits[i]}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-output.txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;output.txt&#34;&gt;0: apple
1: banana
2: mango
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html#for-loops&#34;&gt;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html#for-loops&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>4.1. for-loop (collection)</title>
      <link>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/4.1.for-loop-collection/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Nov 2021 09:56:03 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://syntax-compare.github.io/compare/kotlin/4.1.for-loop-collection/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-kotlin&#34; data-lang=&#34;kotlin&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; fruits = listOf(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;apple&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;banana&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;mango&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (fruit &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; fruits) {
    println(fruit)
}

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// option 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;fruits.forEach { fruit &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    println(fruit)
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-output.txt&#34; data-lang=&#34;output.txt&#34;&gt;apple
banana
mango
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reference&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/iterators.html&#34;&gt;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/iterators.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html#for-loops&#34;&gt;https://kotlinlang.org/docs/control-flow.html#for-loops&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
    
